Verified the status of the display manager.
Confirmed the X session environment variable.
Displayed running X-related processes.
✅ Conclusion
The experiment was successfully completed. Virtual terminals, display managers, X clients, and window managers were explored effectively. This experiment provided practical understanding of Linux system interfaces and graphical session management.
